values: I'm deleting this. Its stupid and full of bad memories. bye guys

OMG! I'm alive! haha. I almost forgot about this stupid journal. Funny huh? Well I'm alive. But I no longer live in Florida. Me and Zane are still together, and going on 9 strong months :) We left florida this past tuesday and I love it where we are now. I met his mommy shes such a sweetheart. Ummm not much new has happened. My life was pretty shitty there for a minute. I was homeless and stuff. But now I have a home and I'm much happier and better off here. I miss all you fools in the sunshine state! and all of my old buddies up in massachusetts. keep in touch guys. my email is Ihavenicepants@yahoo.com. please feel free to send me annoying emails all the time!! leave your email addy if you want me to keep in touch <3 -amy
